{"tid":135124,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"《暑假取西經》今個暑假有無人有興趣踩單車去西藏？","createTime":"2017-02-26T06:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T05:19:08.000Z","uid":73593,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16d6b51e0c18bde677e3dd8199456b99b188744b","tid":135124,"uid":73593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:16:48.000Z","msg":"想問下今個暑假有無人有興趣踩單車去西藏？<br />\n<br />\n我打算黎緊呢個暑假就會由香港出發<br />\n睇下呢到有無其他人都想去/已經plan左<br />\n會唔會揾到個伴一齊出發🙇🏿🙇🏿🙇🏿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c70e8c3c2bc7ad67e5307d30d27cc9dc696f83","tid":135124,"uid":52084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"巴打大約幾月岀發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc94b54688387407397813ee9fe708c8321f7ca","tid":135124,"uid":73593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打大約幾月岀發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該五月尾六月頭"},{"pid":"51dcef65dc29f703c613e464ca0c4c15b92f92c3","tid":135124,"uid":52084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打大約幾月岀發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該五月尾六月頭</blockquote><br />\n我八月頭要翻到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五月頭有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eded664760b369f58b0d3480c8308deb816b0279","tid":135124,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"由香港踩去雲林or四川途中搵住宿好麻煩喎<br />\n好多都唔受香港人住<br />\n<br />\n利申:踩過"},{"pid":"77194348bf9a507bd25d40dfe0243e7da390c3af","tid":135124,"uid":87009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c