uid":73593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打大約幾月岀發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該五月尾六月頭</blockquote><br />\n我八月頭要翻到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n五月頭有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最快都要五月中，因為五月頭屋企有啲事<br />\n不過其實就六月頭出發八月頭應該都返到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你平時有無踩開單車？</blockquote><br />\n無踩開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過都叫做有間中跑下步嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六月頭岀發太趕，淆淆地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想預鬆d時間<br />\n我見丹尼爾騎到拉薩都要差唔多60日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五月中至尾出發會唔會好啲？<br />\n可以PM再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14664df5479dd4f9a8364728ca0c141824643d0","tid":135124,"uid":73593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由香港踩去雲林or四川途中搵住宿好麻煩喎<br />\n好多都唔受香港人住<br />\n<br />\n利申:踩過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無原因唔受香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n旅館有部機係公安比<br />\n用黎掃描身分證<br />\n但掃唔到回鄉卡<br />\n一係你就去貴既酒店<br />\n一係就屌佢話要報公安</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁真係要睇下資料先"},{"pid":"eba250a09c29bc703516eb72a5ad8170f49e4ba0","tid":135124,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"我5月頭出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為香港人要住涉外賓館 有限制"},{"pid":"390dee27e36cfa71bc271357ea53dff6ca434633","tid":135124,"uid":52084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited